content: That's really helpful! I'll make sure to keep those tips in mind when reaching out to influencers in the fitness niche. By the way, I've been meaning to clean up my Facebook friends list, and on July 20th, I spent about an hour going through my list and unfriending around 30 people I no longer keep in touch with. I also updated my Facebook profile picture that day, which got 21 comments and 35 likes. Do you have any advice on how to optimize my Facebook profile and increase engagement?
